      <pubDate>Mon, 23 Sep 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <description>&lt;div class="wi_fic_desc" property="description"&gt;&lt;p&gt;When Riley’s sister Nancy finds out he secretly wears girl clothes, she makes a plan for a night that would change his life forever.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;/div&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;h3&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.scribblehub.com/read/969413-sisters/chapter/1231674/"&gt;&lt;div class="chapter-title"&gt;Chapter 1&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;div class="chp_raw" id="chp_raw"&gt;&lt;p&gt;Finally I’m home from school. No more studying, no more sports, finally I get to be in my own world after a rough week...and I know just what to do to make myself feel better!&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;For years I’ve snuck in to my older sisters room and put on her clothes...no, I don’t know why! And I’m definitely not a creep! It just feels kinda nice...? Going from a scrawny awkward sophomore to something else...just feels right?&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;A-anyway back to the task at hand.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;I ran up stairs and in to my sister Nancy’s room. I raided her dirty clothes per usual and picked out a bra, panties, shorts, and a crop top.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Nancy and I are about the same size which is good because that way I won’t stretch out her clothes.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;In the mirror, I see some lame ass perfect son...it’s just never felt quite right going through the motions just to be normal.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Then again dressing up in my sisters stuff really isn’t that normal now is it?&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;I undressed and slowly slid on the bra and panties making sure to tuck in my junk as i did, then I put on the rest of the ensemble and took a look in her full length mirror.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;This is my favorite part. I just get this rush of serotonin, I’m not quite sure why but it doesn’t matter. Looking myself up and down, feeling confident and just, really good. Usually I go in my room after and just chill in the clothes, but this time I fucked up.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;I left my clothes on Nancy’s floor...&lt;/p&gt; &lt;/div&gt;</description>
